  "description": "Pi package for Elixir projects: Mix post-edit checks, Expert LSP bridge, commands, LLM tools, and Elixir/Phoenix/Ecto/OTP skills.",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "keywords": [
    "pi-package",
    "pi",
    "elixir",
